The recommendation to enable secure desktop as a best practice conflicts with NIST's recommendation to allow pasting of passwords to enable/encourage complex passwords...
o	https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/SpecialPublications/NIST.SP.800-63b.pdf?page=24
o	https://www.thesslstore.com/blog/nist-password-pasting/
o	https://www.ncsc.gov.uk/blog-post/let-them-paste-passwords





